{
  "stem": "19550.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the bags, many of them, you know, they just thrown about, either almost voluntarily or because they were being driven and beaten into the, into the cars, and they just lost it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People run back to try to catch it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And  [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my-- personally, my whole preoccupation was with how do I make my family as, as-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] how do I make it as bearable as possible?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Approximately how many people were in this cattle car with you?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "80.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We propped up our mother against in one corner with my little sister in front of her and all of us, all my sisters, sort of surrounding them, barely enough room to stand.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people would fall down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, people died in, in the car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] on our way for, I think, three nights.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When we crossed what used to be the old Czech border or a little past it, there was a town called Kosice, K-O-S-I-C-I-E in, in Slovakian, but in, in Hungarian, it was known as Kassa, K-A-- K-A-S-S-A.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there the Hungarian police formally handed us over to the SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The, the trip was probably the most inhuman aspect of, of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] impossible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know how any of us survived it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in Poland, and I'm trying to remember now what the name of the town was where we stood, where the train was halted for whatever the reason.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had spoken to one of the guards.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
